title: Day 392
content:
# Day 392

This is going to be a short one because my eyes hurt from staring at screens all day.

Light is everything. Get more sunlight if you want to be healthy. Not having sunlight is worse for you than smoking everyday.

<iframe src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-U26QAlfp9Y%3Ffeature%3Doembed&display_name=YouTube&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-U26QAlfp9Y&image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-U26QAlfp9Y%2Fhqdefault.jpg&key=a19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07&type=text%2Fhtml&schema=youtube" title="" height="480" width="854"></iframe>

The comment section in that video is worth the scroll. It is quite hilarious.

On another note I did a great podcast today with Mike from River about The Blocksize Wars. Looking forward to getting that one out and having Mike back on to discuss The Book Of Satoshi next.

Finally, walk more. Yes that is the advice. WALK MORE!

See you tomorrow anon for a longer post but for now my eyes hurt from staring at a screen all day.

4/18/23

Conor Jay Chepenik
